WEBVTT

00:00.031 --> 00:02.166
Death to the Medicis!

00:02.836 --> 00:04.336
I must return to the palace.

00:04.404 --> 00:09.575
Citizens of Florence, I put
the fate of our Republic

00:09.642 --> 00:11.510
in your hands.

00:11.578 --> 00:14.013
Palle!
The Medici rallying cry.

00:14.080 --> 00:15.681
We apprehend
the Pazzi traitors.

00:15.749 --> 00:17.282
<i>You dare kill a cardinal?</i>

00:17.350 --> 00:20.252
We will dangle you
in your Sunday best.

00:20.320 --> 00:22.521
You let Riario take Nico?

00:22.589 --> 00:24.456
I was supposed
to be on that ship.

00:24.524 --> 00:25.724
There's someone
that can help.

00:25.792 --> 00:28.193
There is a man
named Vespucci.

00:28.261 --> 00:30.696
You wish to sail west
but the Vatican have stolen your ship.

00:30.764 --> 00:32.765
We steal one of theirs.

00:32.832 --> 00:36.168
You seek an alliance with us
against France?

00:36.236 --> 00:37.436
How may we be of service?

00:37.504 --> 00:39.171
Rome's aggression
will not stop.

00:39.239 --> 00:40.672
Did this belong
to your grandfather?

00:40.740 --> 00:42.207
Take it with you
on your journey.

00:42.275 --> 00:45.477
<i>Brothers whose blood flows</i>
<i>in each other's veins.</i>

00:46.746 --> 00:48.547
♪

